Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Latitude 303 Logistics provides a unique combination of freeway access and frontage along Loop 303 in Glendale, Arizona. This superb location not only provides excellent visibility from the Loop 303, it also guarantees access to an unmatched labor market in the West Valley of Metro Phoenix. 

This two building, Class A development sits within the most exciting industrial corridor in the Valley, home to numerous large name brand users, offering unmatched access to multiple freeways that connect your supply chain to major ports and numerous cities in all directions in the region. 

Consisting of ±900,000 SF available for lease, Latitude 303 Logistics offers a tremendous opportunity for users to take advantage of the benefits of the hottest industrial corridor in Maricopa County, the United States’ fastest growing county.
